Quadding - I do this all the time in Fire - not as much anymore since I maxxed my AA's but I still do it to help powerlevel guildmates. 72% AA exp from a quad is no laughing matter.<br>
<br>
Root/Snares - I root and snare a lot in certain elemental planes during the raid. One of the prime examples is Plane of Earth, the rock ring. I'll snare as many mobs as I can and get aggro on them till the chanters can mez them (People know what I'm talking about if I'm there)<br>
<br>
PBAE - Plane of Earth and Plane of Water - You guys know what I'm talking about if you are there.<br>
<br>
Rains - If you're not already casting rains on boss's then you really should try. I use rains all the time. Casting for example Tears of marr, then casting ADOI and Ice Spear = HUGE DPS with very little aggro as compared to ONE Strike of Sol Cast.<br>
<br>
